## Encoding Decisions

| Element | Decision |
|---|---|
| Schema | TEI All (tei_all.rng), as specified in template |
| Namespace | `http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0` |
| Footnotes | Encoded in `<back>` as `<note>` elements with xml:id; referenced inline with `<ref>` |
| Hyphenated line-breaks | Normalized (hyphens from line-wrapping removed; preserved only where meaningful) |
| Original page breaks | Marked with `<pb n="X"/>` to preserve pagination |
| Special characters | Encoded as Unicode (UTF-8); no numeric entities unless necessary |

